FBIS3-54225 "drnes016_n_94005" FBIS-NES-94-016 Document Type:Daily Report 25 Jan 1994 LEBANON Al-Hirawi, Birri Leave for Syria To Offer Condolences NC2501102494 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon in Arabic 0945 GMT 25 Jan 94 NC2501102494 (Clandestine) Radio Free Lebanon Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] President Ilyas al-Hirawi left Beirut at 1130 today for al-Qardahah [in Syria] to offer condolences to Syrian President Hafiz al-Asad on the death of his son, Basil. The president, accompanied by Chamber of Deputies Speaker Nabih Birri, left Beirut airport on a private plane.
